<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>梦想 on 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E6%A2%A6%E6%83%B3/</link><description>Recent content in 梦想 on 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2006 - 2025 &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://www.eallion.com/copyright/' target='_blank'>eallion.com&lt;/a> All Rights Reserved&lt;/span>. &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://beian.miit.gov.cn/' target='_blank'>浙ICP备16031768号-2&lt;/a>&lt;/span></copyright><lastBuildDate>Thu, 10 Dec 2015 09:06:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E6%A2%A6%E6%83%B3/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><follow_challenge><feedId>42331815237783556</feedId><userId>41909911558319104</userId></follow_challenge><item><title>起床</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/get-up/</link><pubDate>Thu, 10 Dec 2015 09:06:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/get-up/</guid><description>闹钟唤醒沉睡的身体，但梦想才是点燃灵魂的火种。真正怀揣梦想的人早已在黎明前启程，因为他们的热情永不休眠！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/get-up/featured.png"/></item><item><title>其实我是比较喜欢坐火车</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/train-journey/</link><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jan 2011 08:30:13 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/train-journey/</guid><description>韩寒的《他人的生活》道出了普通人春运归乡的艰辛，引发共鸣。从小渴望坐火车看世界的梦想，在家乡通火车后才逐渐实现，但初次体验已被嘈杂拥挤冲淡，唯独记得十岁时乘独木舟过江的紧张与豪情。最近一次站票25小时的经历虽苦，却因结识旅伴而难忘。火车承载着对远方的永恒向往，真正的旅行是修行而非观光。春运难题仍是游子心中之痛，愿归乡者平安抵达。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/train-journey/featured.png"/></item><item><title>有关于梦想</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/aboutdream/</link><pubDate>Sun, 04 Apr 2010 22:27:17 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/aboutdream/</guid><description>纪录片《待业青年》揭示了梦想的消逝，引发对童年梦想的回忆。曾痴迷电脑的神奇功能，甚至幻想通过五笔字入侵白宫，这份执着最终促成了现在的博客。然而，那些荒诞的梦想，如写书感化邪教徒或战胜艾滋，经分析后显得不切实际。如今，梦想已变得简单而实际，比如每周玩两局 CS 或看一集《迷失》。梦想虽小，却真实可触！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/aboutdream/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>